        <mj-spacer height="16px" />
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" css-class="light_img" width="150px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/gp-logo-grey.png" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" alt="" />
        
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 0px" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 2px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
            ">Did you know that the King of the UK receives daily updates on government affairs through a red dispatch box every morning?</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
            "><strong>On 7th Jan 2025 edition:</strong> </p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ Taiwan suspects Chinese vessel</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ Sarkozy on trial</p>
          <p style="
              font-size: 16px;
              line-height: 1.4;
              padding-left: 10px;
            ">→ Why did Ukraine move Christmas to the 25th?</p>
         
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="0px 0px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-spacer height="10px"></mj-spacer>
    <!-- Spotlight -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_fsection" background-color="#ffffff" css-class="mj_fsection">
      <mj-column background-color="#ffffff" width="100%">
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px 0px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="white">
          <h2 style="
          color:#06266D;
            text-align: left;
            letter-spacing:6px;
            border-bottom:2px solid #06266D;
            text-transform:uppercase;
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 300;
              padding: 18px 8px 10px 8px; 
              
            ">SPOTLIGHT</h2>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section> 
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500; margin-top:2px !important">A surprise assault
</h2> 
        </mj-text>
         <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com/email/images/gp-jan-7-1.jpg" alt="A surprise assault" href="https://www.geopoliticalsummary.com" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">Ukraine has launched a <a target="_blank" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-07-01-2025-h1-1-counterattack">counterattack</a> in Russia’s Kursk region, targeting multiple locations in a surprise assault. Ukrainian forces, which have held parts of Kursk since August, face resistance from Russian and North Korean troops. Kyiv claims its offensive delivers justice, while Moscow asserts its units repelled the attack near Berdin. The head of the Ukrainian Presidential Office, Andriy Yermak, said, “Kursk region, good news, Russia is getting what it deserves.” The Ukraine military has not publicly confirmed the operation.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4; filter: blur(5px)">The Russian Defense Ministry claims to have repelled two assaults. Ukraine aims to strengthen its position before potential negotiations, while Russia questions the strategy behind the incursion. Hundreds of <a target="_blank" href="https://link.geopoliticalsummary.com/gs-07-01-2025-h1-2-north-koreans-have-died">North Koreans have died</a> so far in the Makhnovka village in Kursk. Both sides have taken a lot of losses this winter and are claiming to be ready to end the war; the more significant issue is the agreement on the conditions on how to end the war.</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-spacer height="15px"></mj-spacer>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>